@startuml
actor Penjual
participant View
participant Controller
participant Model
participant Database

Penjual -> View : Akses halaman Daftar Pesanan\nPilih pesanan siap dikirim\nKlik "Cetak Label Pengiriman"
View -> Controller : GET /seller/orders/{id}/label

Controller -> Model : get shipping data(id)
Model -> Database : query (Alamat Pembeli, Ekspedisi, Resi, Penjual)
Database --> Model : result
Model --> Controller : result

Controller -> Controller : Generate layout Label Pengiriman
Controller --> View : Return HTML/PDF Label
View --> Penjual : Tampilkan layout untuk dicetak

Penjual -> View : Kirim perintah cetak ke Printer\nTempelkan label pada paket
@enduml
